And I too was sceptical about Strike... but now that the casting cost is down to 800, that puts the efficiency at 3.25, which sounds like a fair trade to me. Think about the dps... yikes...<br>
<br>
2700 base damage<br>
+ 810 (focus ~10% average + 20% enhanced DD song)<br>
+ 405 (SCFM average)<br>
= 3915 nominal yield<br>
/4 seconds casting<br>
= 978 nominal dps<br>
<br>
That's approaching manaburn dps, and at about 50% better efficiency. Probably more like double efficiency when you account for specialization. Looks good to me.<br>
