The only really useful aa's for warriors are the HP adding and ae taunt.  It's true that with the new aa's, warriors will get a significant boost in hp (their main stat)....but wizards will be getting a significant boost in effective mana as well (their main stat).....remember that in addition to increased int, there is also acsm with effectively gives you more mana.<br>
